    <SectionTitle Id="disabled" Title="Disabled" />
    <p>Set the <code>Enabled</code> parameter to <code>false</code> in order to give the input a grayed out appearance and make it not interactable.</p>
    <Demo Type="typeof(HxInputRange_Demo_Disabled)" />

    <SectionTitle Id="min-max" Title="Min and max" />
    <p>By default, the component's value is kept between <code>0</code> and <code>100</code>, you may adjust these values by setting the <code>Min</code> and <code>Max</code> parameters.</p>
    <Demo Type="typeof(HxInputRange_Demo_MinMax)" />

    <SectionTitle Id="steps" Title="Steps" />
    <p>By default, <code>HxInputRange</code> "snaps" to integer values. To change this, you can supply a value to the <code>Step</code> parameter.</p>
    <Demo Type="typeof(HxInputRange_Demo_Steps)" />

    <SectionTitle Id="bind-event" Title="Bind event" />
    <p>Decides whether the <code>Value</code> is going to be updated <code>onchange</code> or <code>oninput</code> (immediately). Default is <code>BindEvent.OnChange</code>.</p>
    <Demo Type="typeof(HxInputRange_Demo_BindEvent)" />

